{"tid":1081298,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"保守黨逾10人有意角逐相位   約翰遜高文浩大熱","createTime":"2019-03-28T08:08:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T10:54:20.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3c1ac53118563c09b067818d3bd0f1cee4f8e215","tid":1081298,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T08:08:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190328/large/1553747674_d454.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190328%2Flarge%2F1553747674_d454.jpg&h=c3ca812a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國首相文翠珊以下台換取保守黨議員支持她的脫歐協議，如果脫歐協議獲通過，新黨魁之爭會在5月22日後展開。多位保守黨黨員均蠢蠢欲動，外界猜測接任黨魁的大熱人選是保守黨內脫歐派的前外相約翰遜（Boris Johnson）、環境大臣高文浩（Michael Gove）和內政大臣賈偉德（Sajid Javid）。<br />\n<br />\n內閣有多達8位官員預料會參選，包括高文浩、賈偉德及外相侯俊偉（Jeremy Hunt），衞生大臣夏國賢（Matt Hancock）、財政部首席秘書卓慧思（Liz Truss）、國防大臣韋廉信（Gavin Williamson）和國際發展大臣莫佩琳（Penny Mordaunt）都被指有意接棒。至於文翠珊心腹、就業及退休保障大臣盧綺婷（Amber Rudd）則仍在考慮是否參選。<br />\n<br />\n非內閣成員、曾與文翠珊在2016年黨魁之爭對決的下議院領袖利雅華（Andrea Leadsom）、脫歐派領軍人物約翰遜和前脫歐事務大臣藍韜文（Dominic Raab）亦有可能參選。一位議員周三形容黨魁戰將變得非常激烈：「這將會有如《賓虛》一樣的場面－－單是演員就有數千人。」<br />\n<br />\n博彩公司立博（Ladbrokes）周三晚將高文浩和約翰遜並列為大熱人選，賠率是1賠4，緊隨其後的是侯俊偉，而藍韜文和賈偉德的賠率則僅1賠10。<br />\n<br />\n如果文翠珊的協議獲得通過，英國將會在5月22日離開歐盟，她亦會辭任保守黨領袖，但會留任至選出繼任人為止。任何保守黨員也需要兩名黨友提名才可以參選，之後保守黨314名國議員會進行不記名投票，選出兩名候選人，兩人會向黨員演說及全國拉票爭取12.5萬黨員的支持。<br />\n<br />\n保守黨消息指，整個黨魁選舉預料需時4至6周，可能在7月中才會選出黨魁。文翠珊原訂今年6月28至29日到大阪出席20國集團峯會（G20），可能是最後一次在國際舞台上亮相。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》"},{"pid":"b580b1c0d4c47fc29081cc20d09f20b368c595d2","tid":1081298,"uid":63846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T08:12:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GGgiGtJk7MA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGGgiGtJk7MA&d=pW%2BpET2SRZmQ0hv433X7AHJTAtm2oKGHsrawk8oVPbs%3D&h=b3263b93\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GGgiGtJk7MA</a><br />\n<br />\nGove <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89d06bdf3e9faa68fac205bc29ebb4df914256c0","tid":1081298,"uid":116630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T08:47:17.000Z","msg":"肯定完到 brixit? 而家就選相啦？"},{"pid":"fb72262548bc77f4e34177ace3f476cda5d97a33","tid":1081298,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T10:12:26.000Z","msg":"點解明明有莊漢生唔用係都要約翰遜<br />\n同金馬倫一樣死都要叫卡梅倫"},{"pid":"05706d2db454847958f7d4dde395c734f7c9e3a3","tid":1081298,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb72262548bc77f4e34177ace3f476cda5d97a33","tid":1081298,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T10:12:26.000Z","msg":"點解明明有莊漢生唔用係都要約翰遜<br />\n同金馬倫一樣死都要叫卡梅倫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T10:16:11.000Z","msg":"英國官方譯名係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"690a6367bfa9407e59275fb492ca2af468fd2bf1","tid":1081298,"uid":174766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T10:20:54.000Z","msg":"Penny Mordaunt<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thetimes.co.uk/imageserver/image/methode%2Ftimes%2Fprod%2Fweb%2Fbin%2F16612396-c57f-11e7-92dc-06edfbca4aab.jpg?crop=2108%2C3162%2C0%2C0&amp;resize=640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.co.uk%2Fimageserver%2Fimage%2Fmethode%252Ftimes%252Fprod%252Fweb%252Fbin%252F16612396-c57f-11e7-92dc-06edfbca4aab.jpg%3Fcrop%3D2108%252C3162%252C0%252C0%26resize%3D640&h=b388c9c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有肉地啪啪聲"},{"pid":"75080306f86f95932016dcd31344cb0662c48051","tid":1081298,"uid":174766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"690a6367bfa9407e59275fb492ca2af468fd2bf1","tid":1081298,"uid":174766,"like